> The placement here is because we can't call ravb_rx_ring_refill() until
> priv->dirty_rx[q] has been zero'd.
> 
> The init order right now is actually:
>   RX page pool
>   RX buffers
>   TX SKBs
>   RX descriptors
>   RX ring buffer
>   TX descriptors
> 
> So maybe this should be re-ordered.
